cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IT

This paper deals with video understanding and action recognition, which are typically studied in the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. The paper also proposes a novel approach using teacher-student method, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the use of compressed video data, which involves compression techniques and information theory, making the information theory (cs.IT) sub-category a likely fit as well.
